this LinkEventDefinition represents a 'throw' or 'source' LinkEventDefinition.</rdfs:comment>
</owl:ObjectProperty>

<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="https://www.irit.fr/recherches/MELODI/ontologies/BBO#has_state">
